<!-- 使用者詳情說明視窗 -->
<div class="fixed inset-0 bg-black bg-opacity-50 z-[9999] flex items-center justify-center p-4">
    <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-2xl max-w-lg w-full max-h-[70vh] overflow-hidden">
        <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-600 to-blue-700 px-6 py-4 text-white">
            <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
                <div class="flex items-center space-x-3">
                    <i data-lucide="help-circle" class="w-5 h-5"></i>
                    <h3 class="text-lg font-bold">人員詳情說明</h3>
                </div>
                <button onclick="closeHelp()" class="text-white hover:text-blue-200 transition-colors">
                    <i data-lucide="x" class="w-5 h-5"></i>
                </button>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="p-6 overflow-y-auto max-h-[calc(70vh-120px)]">
            <div class="space-y-4">
                <div>
                    <h4 class="font-semibold text-slate-800 mb-2 flex items-center">
                        <i data-lucide="info" class="w-4 h-4 mr-2 text-blue-600"></i>操作說明
                    </h4>
                    <ul class="space-y-1 text-sm text-slate-600">
                        <li>• <strong>編輯</strong>：點擊「編輯」按鈕修改人員資訊</li>
                        <li>• <strong>關閉</strong>：點擊「關閉」按鈕或右上角 X 關閉視窗</li>
                        <li>• <strong>頭像</strong>：如無頭像則顯示姓名首字母</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                
                <div>
                    <h4 class="font-semibold text-slate-800 mb-2 flex items-center">
                        <i data-lucide="eye" class="w-4 h-4 mr-2 text-green-600"></i>資訊顯示
                    </h4>
                    <p class="text-sm text-slate-600">
                        此頁面顯示人員的完整資訊，包括基本資料、組織歸屬、角色權限等。所有資訊均為唯讀，如需修改請點擊「編輯」按鈕。
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
